<date box="[421,452,1506,1535]" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">
<number box="[421,437,1506,1535]" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" value="2.0">2</number>
x
</date>
longer than wide. Venter yellow except light brown openings and epigastric furrows.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="23.[104,796,1653,1756]" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">
